column5: Check out the link. It is in Japanese, but you dont need to understand what is being said. Just watch the video, and put yourself in the place of any of those drivers, caught in the maelstrom http://www.win7news.net/YH6XYS/110811-Tsunami
crazy stuff  it's a real good thing that guy ran back to shut the door on his vehicle.
wow that is some absolutely crazy footage. At one point I was thinking...ok, climb out window, hop across those skids floating by "a la frogger", and climb the tallest tree around
